		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="398" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">机关阵列瞄准玩家，发射激光轰击地面，造成<span color="#bababa">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">机关阵列化成火箭升空，随后瞄准，重重坠落，造成<span color="#bababa">91.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="422" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">机关阵列化作一个旋转的锯片，倏的切向玩家，造成<span color="#bababa">58.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffcebf">生命值达30%<span color="#ffffff">时或耗时较久后，机关阵列用自己的立方分裂出去召唤</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffffff">遗迹机兵</span><span color="#ffffff">，自己则处于无敌状态，击败被高亮的遗迹机兵以使其虚弱20s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="895" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当机兵存在过久、虚弱时间已到后，机关阵列回收自己的4个机兵，退出无敌状态，重新变为成本体。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">机关阵列化作一把大剑，扫向玩家，造成<span color="#bababa">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">机关阵列化作一个巨大正方体，不断滚向玩家，滚动不造成伤害，到达玩家处猛烈爆炸，造成<span color="#bababa">75%</span><span>伤害，若滚动时间耗尽，同样爆炸，但造成</span><span color="#bababa">91.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/恒常机关阵列.assets/Image_14.png')" x="721" y="138">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/恒常机关阵列.assets/Image_15.png')" x="720" y="361">
