		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">机关阵列展开自身，从核心处持续发射激光，持续造成<span color="#b8b8b8">33.3%</span><span>伤害。跑太远或绕后都会使其停止。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#96673d" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#96673d">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1068" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="432" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">遗迹机兵：只有被高亮的能击败，其他锁血；遗迹机兵在机关阵列虚弱后假死，机关阵列死亡后才真正死亡并产球。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
